room_title: Escape room "Space Escape" by Wolff Escapes in Putnam
room_description: You've just arrived at the space station. A few hours later, the trajectory of the station intersected the asteroidal belt. The station has received substantial damage. The control system almost completely remained in non-working state. Security system alerts you on the approaching giant asteroid, which will completely destroy the station. You have just an hour left to reach the escape pod.
